<help general languages>

The language command can be used to change your preferred
language.  Full support for languages other than english is
not guaranteed, but we will do the best we can.  If you would
like to help with translation to another language, please see
me (greear@cyberhighway.net) and I'll show you how you can
help!!

Languages supported so far:  English(full), Spanish(partial),
      Portugues(very little)

Syntax:  language [language_choice]

Example:  language Spanish

<color=red>
See Also:  topics
</color></help>
